00:00:33.820 --> 00:00:35.780
=Lust and Lies=

00:01:07.079 --> 00:01:07.640
Step aside.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.040
I can let you take her,

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:11.239
but you have

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:12.959
to cooperate with me.

00:01:36.500 --> 00:01:38.100
=Episode 21=

00:01:39.079 --> 00:01:40.190
This is a surprising turn of events.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:41.400
It used to be

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.359
just Feifei and me meeting here.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:44.480
But today,

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.840
it's the two of us.

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:51.439
She doesn't need to come to you anymore.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:55.640
She's already told me everything between you two.

00:01:57.719 --> 00:01:59.079
You're old news.

00:02:26.639 --> 00:02:27.159
So, tell me.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:29.000
How do you want to cooperate?

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.199
Even though
you exposed Huo Beishan's crimes,

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.240
he still commands
100,000 Huo Army soldiers.

00:02:34.919 --> 00:02:36.080
Your chances of winning

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:36.960
aren't great.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:38.919
I know.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:41.780
You've already bribed
a good portion of the Huo Army.

00:02:47.439 --> 00:02:49.280
I can send my troops to back you up.

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:51.680
What do you want in return?

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.240
I want

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:58.520
the Huo family to fall.

00:02:59.639 --> 00:03:02.240
I want the Sheng family to gain

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.800
military power too.

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:09.919
With me on your side,

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:11.680
your odds will improve a lot.

00:03:12.039 --> 00:03:13.240
This benefits both

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.479
you and me.

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:16.000
Deal.

00:03:21.479 --> 00:03:24.159
Well then, here's to a successful partnership.

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:31.520
These belong to Feifei, right?

00:03:33.479 --> 00:03:34.400
I'll take care of them for her.

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:38.120
Young Marshal Huo,

00:03:38.370 --> 00:03:40.199
you shouldn't help yourself
to things that aren't yours.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.879
Who are you to keep her things?

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:03.639
Where did all this come from?

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.439
These belong to you, right?

00:04:06.319 --> 00:04:07.439
They were at Sheng Weilian's place.

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:10.639
These should be Liu Yiyi's.

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:12.080
They often met there in secret.

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:20.800
When I was a child,

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:22.800
I played with knives.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:24.879
I never played with dolls.

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:34.839
We've grown up surrounded by hatred.

00:04:41.639 --> 00:04:42.680
Marry me once all of this

00:04:44.040 --> 00:04:44.879
is over.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:48.680
We'll leave Sucheng to start a new life.

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:58.560
We'll buy a small house together.

00:04:58.879 --> 00:05:01.319
Work at sunrise, rest at sunset.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.680
Three simple meals a day,

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:03.759
plain and humble.

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.800
Living the simplest life.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:08.399
Then, we'll have children

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.319
and grow old together.

