00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:01.759
Huo Xiu…

00:08:10.399 --> 00:08:12.040
Amitabha…

00:08:12.279 --> 00:08:13.560
Amitabha…

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.199
Amitabha…

00:08:15.839 --> 00:08:17.240
Amitabha…

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:19.120
Madam,

00:08:19.319 --> 00:08:20.480
Miss Qingwan sent me.

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.480
Tell her

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.199
not to worry about me

00:08:29.839 --> 00:08:30.959
and to take care of herself.

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:34.120
Madam, the Huo family is beyond saving.

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:36.000
I know.

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:39.600
I'm the lady of the Huo family.

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:42.120
I will never

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:45.559
leave the Huo family.

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:53.639
Since you've made up your mind,

00:08:53.879 --> 00:08:54.799
once you step out that door,

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:56.000
there's no turning back.

00:08:57.559 --> 00:08:59.120
May this help ease your suffering.

00:09:32.679 --> 00:09:35.000
You're the only bloodline
your mother left behind.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:38.559
Having you around

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:41.399
feels like she's still here.

00:09:43.960 --> 00:09:45.799
But I still lost the gamble.

00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:51.799
In the end,

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:54.879
I brought trouble upon myself.

00:09:56.480 --> 00:09:58.039
You kept me close,

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:01.639
so you should've known
this day would come.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:09.039
Huo Xiu,

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:14.120
I once considered

00:10:15.879 --> 00:10:17.799
letting you take control
of the Huo Army.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.720
The Huo Army?

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:27.279
This was once the Gu family.

00:10:28.279 --> 00:10:31.039
Your Huo Army used to be the Gu Army!

00:10:37.190 --> 00:10:37.799
And one more thing.

00:10:41.759 --> 00:10:43.279
My family name is Gu,

00:10:44.879 --> 00:10:46.279
not Huo.

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.080
If I'd known this,

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:56.360
I should have killed
all of you back then.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.960
That Ruan Feifei,

00:11:01.159 --> 00:11:02.600
is she already dead?

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:06.120
I won't give you
another chance to hurt her.

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:15.240
Why didn't you leave?

00:11:16.440 --> 00:11:17.879
Get out of here!

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:41.639
Beishan…

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:43.399
Why didn't you leave?

00:11:44.159 --> 00:11:45.679
We're husband and wife.

00:11:46.879 --> 00:11:48.960
We share life and death.

00:11:49.799 --> 00:11:51.360
And to think, my whole life

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.879
I never once looked you in the eye…

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:08.480
Madam.

00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:10.159
Stay away.

00:12:11.639 --> 00:12:13.600
Can you promise me one thing?

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:15.879
Name it.

00:12:19.159 --> 00:12:20.840
Take care of Qingwan.

00:12:22.679 --> 00:12:23.879
Protect her

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:28.279
for the rest of your life.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:31.480
I will.

